\section{Software design}

\subsection{Python modules}
\ku{\un{smtplib:}}\newline defines an SMTP client session object that can be used to send mail to any Internet machine \newline
\ku{\un{email.mime}}:\newline creates email and MIME objects from scratch\newline
\ku{\un{RPi.GPIO:}} \newline provides a class to control the GPIO on a Raspberry Pi \newline
\ku{\un{NumPy:}}\newline provides converting images to numerical arrays\newline
\ku{\un{OpenCV:}}\newline provides Image processing, face detection and recognition\newline
\ku{\un {Pillow lib:}} \newline provides handling Images


